ArcelorMittal South Africa Swings to First-Quarter Profit of $27 Million

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-05-11T05:07:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-11/arcelormittal-south-africa-swings-to-first-quarter-profit-of-27-million.html
ArcelorMittal South Africa Ltd. (ACL) 
posted attributable earnings of 184 million rand for the three
months to March 31, up from a loss of 496 million rand in the
fourth quarter of 2010.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  